    </div>
  </div>
</div>
```
{{/markdown}}

  <h3 id="cards-details">Details</h3>
  <p>In general cards will be used to display line by line details about a particular object. Replace the div.card-detail element with an ul.card-detail.</p>
  <div class="fn-example">
    <div class="col-md-4">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-heading">
          ACME Publishing
        </div>
        <ul class="card-detail">
          <li>Nonprofit Organization</li>
          <li>Santa Barbara, CA</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
{{#markdown}}
